snippet.textDisplay: I love the concept of recasting the main character--it allows for a lot in the way of storytelling. Kinnaman was awesome. Mackie will be awesome as well. Byron Mann could step in full-time for a prequel season... you could bring in Norman Reedus. Mads Mikkelsen. You could bring in a female lead. Each time the actor changes you get to see a different side, or life, of Kovacs. Anyway, love this series Netflix.
